column2: SELECT m.objid, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 from MyDB.micadogals AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid -- CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n -- JOIN mydb.micadostars AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
